To fix this, we need to add the last word to the list of lines at the end of the function. We can do this by adding the following line of code:

lines.add(text);

This ensures that the last word in the text is added to the list of lines, even if it does not fit on a single line.

Additionally, the function was not checking if the last word in the text is longer than the number of columns. We can fix this by adding a check for this case, using the following code:

if (text.length() > cols) {
